{"tid":1398153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去信到全世界嘅警察部門，評價垃圾黑警表現","createTime":"2019-08-02T16:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:39:10.000Z","uid":5867,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de4db68724131f804e074b19c2b49e9ab8104fc8","tid":1398153,"uid":5867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲打可以寫信到世界各地嘅警察部門，<br />\n就香港垃圾克警嘅表現，以官方形式表達意見，並拒絕技術交流。以孤立行使過分武力，胡亂扣查、拘捕市民嘅仆街。再加上各地嘅警察都話你衰格，可恥嘅時候，嗰啲乜野濕鳩員佐級協會點撚樣出聲，唔好再比佢地班喪盡天良嘅人渣，唔能夠再以自己係世界上其中一支優良嘅警察部門而自居。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7c90907e5408c5eb2b9270d6b1a7e1baf324ff","tid":1398153,"uid":5867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"10ba063942937d914df84df48ecd24ccc91a678e","tid":1398153,"uid":5867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:03:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f1bba57901be92e4fb03325428eff451fa1af80","tid":1398153,"uid":5867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"甚至乎可以建議佢地出埋聯合幫明、譴責，<br />\n效果力量會更大，實行全世都屌鳩班冇撚用，廢柴死黑警。"},{"pid":"417fd3a7cd58766092dcd1470efd500931684921","tid":1398153,"uid":5867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"再推一推"},{"pid":"7695b5f9b298b18361e2e628f8468cbb615ec45e","tid":1398153,"uid":5867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"有冇文宣組見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda30c812d0e8679f7c3007a598d6976dd91ea4b","tid":1398153,"uid":5867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"巴絲打們幫手推推，<br 